OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FKris Jepson went to find out about the
OL,8,Fnew inquiry investigating what
OL,9,Fhappened at Medomsley Detention Centre
OL,11,FA survivor of the Medomsley Detention
OL,12,FCentre abuse scandal says he hopes the
OL,13,Fbeginning of a fresh investigation
OL,14,Finto what happened will allow "the
OL,15,Ftruth" to come out.
OL,17,FEric Sampson, who has waived his right
OL,18,Fto anonymity, was 17 when he was sent
OL,19,Fto Medomsley near , County Durham, in
OL,20,Fthe 1970s.
