OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FHe is one of around 2,000 young men
OL,8,Fand boys to come forward with
OL,9,Fallegations of physical and sexual
OL,10,Fabuse while interned at the facility.
OL,12,FSeveral former officers have been
OL,13,Fconvicted for their actions at the
OL,14,Ffacility following an extensive
OL,15,Fcriminal investigation by Durham
OL,16,FConstabulary, called Operation
OL,17,FSeabrook, which ended in 2023.
