OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FNow, the Prisons and Probation
OL,8,FOmbudsman (PPO) has launched its own
OL,9,Findependent inquiry into what happened
OL,10,Fat the centre and why it was allowed
OL,11,Fto continue for so long.
OL,13,FThe development has been welcomed by
OL,14,FMr Sampson who is hopeful that it will
OL,15,Fallow more information about what
OL,16,Fhappened to come out.
OL,18,F"I think a lot more people will come
OL,19,Fforward," he told ITV Tyne Tees. "The
OL,20,Ftruth needs to come out about what was
OL,21,Fgoing on in these places.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
