OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"I think it has a good chance of
OL,8,Ffinding out a lot more information
OL,9,Fabout what actually went on in there.
OL,11,F"A lot of people are too scared to
OL,12,Fcome forward now because they are
OL,13,Fmarried with families and that. But I
OL,14,Fadvise anybody now to come forward
OL,15,Fwith what they know about the place.
OL,16,FCome forward and tell the story.
OL,18,F"The officers as well who are still
OL,19,Falive and worked in there. They must
OL,20,Fcome forward now and tell the truth."
