OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThose leading the inquiry have made a
OL,8,Fdirect plea for anyone with any
OL,9,Finformation to come forward to assist
OL,10,Ftheir investigations. Mr Sampson said
OL,11,Fhe will speak to investigators himself
OL,12,Fas he seeks answers.
OL,14,F"It totally ruined my life," he said.
OL,15,F"I've never been married and I've got
OL,16,Fno family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
