OL,3,CMedomsley abuse survivor hopes new
OL,4,Cinquiry will uncover 'truth' behind
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"But we realise the Government were
OL,8,Fopposing us on that and we might not
OL,9,Fhave got there so this is the next
OL,10,Fbest thing.
OL,12,F"I actually believe that the amount of
OL,13,Fevidence that will be uncovered by
OL,14,Fthis inquiry will lead to a wider
OL,15,Finquiry not only into Medomsley but
OL,16,Fother detention centres throughout the
OL,17,Fcountry too."
